{"name": "Brick Presbyterian Church Food Pantry ", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* We are open on Wednesdays from 10:00 AM until 2:00 PM. 
* We only ask clients for their first name, zip code, and number of people in the household (and how many are children). 
* Clients pull up to our building under a portico and a representative greets them. 
* They are given a “shopping list” to check off what they’d like to receive and a representative goes inside to fill the order.
